These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, baseball
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the malaysian##1
2. the malaysian is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | coffee     | sprite |
| Nationality   | malaysian | japanese      |
| Sport         | baseball    | skiing      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, video-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, family
2 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Hobby         | video-games      | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | family | thriller    |
| Pet           | goldfish         | frog         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, lawyer
2 different pets are kept: horse, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the videographer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Job         | videographer | lawyer |
| Pet         | goat       | horse       |
| Transport   | trike       | motorbike         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, photography
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, airplane
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage    | cola    | 7up     |
| Hobby       | chess    | photography |
| Transport   | tram | airplane    |

 #################################

 
