.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, disaster
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | disaster   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep          | d&b   |
| Sport         | rugby     | skateboarding |

 